♪Only leaves me with my shadow?♪

285
00:19:05,160 --> 00:19:08,680
♪Yet the intertwining bonds in my life♪

286
00:19:08,880 --> 00:19:12,200
♪Render me blind♪

287
00:19:13,360 --> 00:19:16,880
♪I was once naive and innocent♪

288
00:19:17,280 --> 00:19:20,160
♪Seeking a soul with whom to dance♪

289
00:19:21,320 --> 00:19:25,120
♪Yet my life is like a wisp of smoke♪

290
00:19:25,280 --> 00:19:28,280
♪Scattered by a gust of wind♪

291
00:19:28,560 --> 00:19:31,280
♪In this life, I am not destined to be understood♪

292
00:19:31,600 --> 00:19:33,560
♪But misunderstood♪

293
00:19:33,720 --> 00:19:36,640
♪I do not know sincerity♪

294
00:19:36,800 --> 00:19:41,400
♪If the river of time could flow back to its starting point♪

295
00:19:41,560 --> 00:19:44,760
♪Let's not meet in another life♪

296
00:19:47,320 --> 00:19:51,550
♪Not in another life♪
